<i>( Man Shouts Greeting )</i>

02:11.030 --> 02:15.296
Okay. Perfect.
We're all set for turkey day.

02:15.368 --> 02:19.134
And there'll be plenty of room,
especially without Laurie.

02:19.205 --> 02:21.605
Has anyone heard from her?
Of course not!

02:21.674 --> 02:24.438
I guess respect and courtesy
aren't genetic like...

02:24.511 --> 02:26.843
my slim hips.

02:28.448 --> 02:31.940
Hey, Schotzie, stay away
from my witch sister.

02:32.018 --> 02:35.579
