02:47.333 --> 02:50.166
His parents
still live in that house.

02:50.236 --> 02:53.262
Mrs. Forman, if it helps,
I can inviteJackie to Thanksgiving.

02:53.339 --> 02:56.172
She's bitchy like Laurie.

02:56.242 --> 02:59.302
