to your Thanksgiving dinner...

02:59.379 --> 03:02.314
and I'll bring a date and a
1 2-pack just like the pilgrims.

03:09.956 --> 03:13.392
Hey, guys. Red is gonna flip
when he sees this failing notice.

03:13.459 --> 03:16.360
''To the parent or guardian
of Eric Forman.''

03:16.429 --> 03:18.420
Your son is a complete idiot.

03:23.670 --> 03:27.936
Please kick him out
and raise the foreign boy as your own.

03:30.143 --> 03:33.010
Man, all I did was mess up
on two math quizzes...

03:33.079 --> 03:35.172
but Ms. McGee has to be all-

03:35.248 --> 03:38.217
( Whining ) I'm Ms. McGee.
I wear high heels and fail everybody.

03:39.485 --> 03:41.953
What's that?

03:42.021 --> 03:43.989
That's Ms. McGee.

03:44.057 --> 03:46.787
You hardly changed your voice.

03:48.361 --> 03:50.795
Well, sure, I did.
( Whining ) I'm Ms. McGee.

03:50.863 --> 03:52.797
That's just your voice.

03:54.200 --> 03:58.534
- I'm doing an impression.
- Well, you suck at impressions.

03:58.605 --> 04:01.665
- Okay. Forget it.
- Are you still doing her?

04:02.909 --> 04:05.969
Oh, hey, Red.
Do me a favor. Sign this, huh?

04:06.045 --> 04:08.275
My gym teacher's failing me
'cause I won't wear shorts.

04:08.348 --> 04:11.442
- Why won't you wear shorts?
- Would you wear shorts?

04:11.517 --> 04:13.815
Fine.

04:15.521 --> 04:18.978
- Thank you.
- So, Eric. How's school treating you?

04:19.058 --> 04:22.585
You managing to, uh, keep
from embarrassing yourself?

04:22.662 --> 04:25.790
Yeah. Oh, sure. I've been
buckling down just like you said...

04:25.865 --> 04:28.231
and thinking a little bit
more about my future...

04:28.301 --> 04:30.667
which I believe
you also recommended.

04:31.671 --> 04:33.798
Well, it's good to know...

04:33.873 --> 04:38.572
that 1 7 years of kicking your ass
has finally paid off.

04:41.914 --> 04:44.212
Eric, you didn't have him
sign your failing notice.

04:44.284 --> 04:47.014
Oh, I don't wanna
trouble him with this old thing.

04:47.086 --> 04:50.522
I'll just sign his name
myself, because...

04:50.590 --> 04:53.684
that's how good a son I am.

04:53.760 --> 04:57.696
( Man Singing Blues Rock )

04:57.764 --> 04:59.698
( Gobbling )

04:59.766 --> 05:01.700
Okay, careful. Careful.
Watch the TV.

05:01.768 --> 05:03.929
Okay, this is good.
Perfect. Perfect.

05:05.905 --> 05:08.430
You. Why are you here?

05:10.276 --> 05:13.336
You don't even know
what Thanksgiving is.

05:14.847 --> 05:17.975
I'm here because my host parents
are feeding bums at church.

05:19.686 --> 05:22.120
Charity begins at home, my ass.

05:23.956 --> 05:25.924
<i>( Doorbell Rings )</i>

05:28.461 --> 05:31.760
- Laurie.
- Hey, little brother.

05:31.831 --> 05:35.528
You're back. And you're not
even eight months pregnant.

05:37.236 --> 05:39.363
- Mommy!
- <i>Laurie.!</i>

05:39.439 --> 05:43.102
( Laughs ) Oh, my goodness!
I knew you'd come.

05:43.176 --> 05:47.772
- Hi, Daddy!
- All the phones broken in Chicago?

05:47.847 --> 05:50.213
No. Well, see, I had other plans...

05:50.283 --> 05:52.808
but my date-
I mean, business associate-

05:52.885 --> 05:54.819
had to go be with his wife.

05:54.887 --> 05:57.481
