05:57.557 --> 05:59.548
I'm doin' good!

05:59.625 --> 06:01.593
Okay, well, you know what?

06:01.661 --> 06:04.687
I'm gonna set you a place
right next to me at the big table.

06:04.764 --> 06:07.597
No, Kitty.
I think that seat belongs to Eric.

06:07.667 --> 06:10.568
Me? At the adults' table?

06:14.340 --> 06:16.570
Are you sure I'm ready?

06:16.642 --> 06:19.076
- But, Daddy-
- Maybe before you leave...

06:19.145 --> 06:21.306
you'll be acting
a little more like him.

06:24.450 --> 06:27.476
Yeah!
( Laughing )

06:27.553 --> 06:30.522
I'm the favorite now. Ooh!

06:30.590 --> 06:32.615
Taste that.

06:38.831 --> 06:41.425
Pimp gave ya the holiday off, huh?

06:43.836 --> 06:46.669
Yeah. He replaced me with your mom.

06:48.674 --> 06:50.835
Now it's Thanksgiving.

06:53.546 --> 06:55.480
Hey, Donna.

06:55.548 --> 06:57.482
You know how my dad's proud of me...

06:57.550 --> 07:00.747
- for doing so well in school?
- Even though it's a lie, and you're failing math...

07:00.820 --> 07:03.687
- 'cause you spend all your time with me?
- Yeah. Right. That's-

07:03.756 --> 07:07.123
That's right. Well,just now, right now,
right in there, right now...

07:07.193 --> 07:10.754
Red asked <i>me</i> to
sit at the grown-ups' table.

07:12.465 --> 07:14.592
Wow!

07:14.667 --> 07:18.660
I hear each person over there
gets their own biscuit.

07:18.738 --> 07:21.639
Yeah. Donna, it's glorious.

07:23.943 --> 07:25.877
Donna.

07:25.945 --> 07:29.938
Donna, I want to tell
everyone we're engaged. Tonight.

07:30.016 --> 07:33.474
Tonight? Are you sure?

07:33.553 --> 07:35.578
Yeah, I just-

07:35.655 --> 07:38.624
I just want everyone
to know, you know?

07:38.691 --> 07:41.125
So when the moment's right...

07:41.194 --> 07:43.355
we'll just-we'll tell 'em all.

07:43.429 --> 07:46.193
This is so awesome!

07:46.265 --> 07:48.995
And then,just in case,
we'll run like hell.

07:50.636 --> 07:52.900
- I probably won't wait for you.
- Oh, okay. Yeah.

07:59.812 --> 08:02.337
That's a beautiful table, Kitty.

08:02.415 --> 08:06.647
Well, thank you, Daddy.
So glad that you and Mom could be here.

08:06.719 --> 08:09.051
Well, we have to eat somewhere.

08:10.456 --> 08:14.222
And, Mom, I know that we have had
our ups and downs...

08:14.293 --> 08:16.523
but in honor of this special day...

08:16.596 --> 08:19.531
I would like to tell you
that <i>I</i> am thankful...

08:19.599 --> 08:22.966
that you are my mother,
and I love you.

08:27.640 --> 08:29.972
Isn't there something
you would like to tell me?

08:31.511 --> 08:33.604
Actually, I would like
some more tea.

08:36.115 --> 08:39.448
I'll try and slip
some booze in there...

08:39.519 --> 08:41.645
in the interest of a happy holiday.

08:46.459 --> 08:48.586
So, Thanksgiving.

08:48.661 --> 08:51.596
We celebrate the subjugation
of an indigenous people...

08:51.664 --> 08:54.929
with yams and Underdog floats.

08:55.001 --> 08:57.868
Yeah. I'm mostly celebrating
my pretty new dress.

08:59.171 --> 09:01.765
And so much for talking.

09:03.743 --> 09:06.803
May I wet your whistle, grandpa?

09:06.879 --> 09:09.404
Gonna have to say yes to that.

09:10.516 --> 09:12.814
Well, cannot let this go to waste.

09:12.885 --> 09:15.820
When did they get a houseboy?

09:19.992 --> 09:23.359
<i>( Pounding )</i>

09:24.564 --> 09:26.896
Happy Thanksgiving, Mrs. Forman.

09:26.966 --> 09:29.025
This is my date Carol.

09:29.101 --> 09:31.160
Ms. McGee?

09:36.142 --> 09:38.076
Kelso...

09:38.144 --> 09:40.669
you're dating my math teacher?

09:40.746 --> 09:43.010
No. No, no, no.
We're not <i>dating.</i>

09:43.082 --> 09:45.107
We just have a relationship...

09:45.184 --> 09:48.483
that I thought
we agreed to keep a secret?

09:49.822 --> 09:52.120
Well, um, welcome.

09:52.191 --> 09:55.217
Michael,
she is 1 0 years older than you.

09:55.294 --> 09:57.956
Oh, no, no.
Nine and five-twelfths.

09:58.030 --> 10:00.863
- ( Laughs ) She taught me that.
- Ooh!

10:00.933 --> 10:02.867
- Very good, Michael.
- Thank you.

10:02.935 --> 10:04.869
Okay.

10:04.937 --> 10:07.633
Kelso, how could you bring her?

10:07.707 --> 10:11.700
Oh, relax, man. She's not going to
quiz you or anything.

10:11.777 --> 10:15.577
But if she does,
the square root of zero is zero.

10:15.648 --> 10:19.675
She got me with that last night,
earned herself a free massage.

10:21.821 --> 10:25.450
Um, Ms. McGee,
being that it's a holiday and all...

10:25.524 --> 10:28.493
there are certain math-related...

10:28.561 --> 10:31.155
failing-type things
I'd rather not talk about.

10:31.230 --> 10:34.825
I hear you. There are certain things
I'd like to keep quiet too.

10:34.900 --> 10:38.063
So if anyone from the school board
should ask...

10:38.137 --> 10:40.628
I came alone,
and I left before dessert.

10:43.042 --> 10:45.340
Eric, maybe we should wait
on the big announcement...

10:45.411 --> 10:47.345
now that your math teacher is here.

10:47.413 --> 10:49.347
Oh, no, Donna.
We don't have to worry...

10:49.415 --> 10:51.440
'cause she's not
my math teacher today.

10:51.517 --> 10:54.008
Today she's a cradle-robbing slut.

10:54.086 --> 10:57.283
- Yea, student-teacher relationships!
- Yea!

10:58.524 --> 11:01.925
Hey, Laurie.
Long time no doin' it.

11:04.330 --> 11:06.625
Maybe for you.

11:06.758 --> 11:10.694
So, what time is your date
gonna let you out for recess?

11:12.197 --> 11:15.689
Nice try, Laurie. There's no recess today.
It's Thanksgiving!

11:18.203 --> 11:20.728
Wow, Laurie.

11:20.806 --> 11:24.503
( Laughs ) Yeah, me and her
really had something, huh?

11:24.576 --> 11:27.067
Yeah. Ointment
took care of that, though, right?

11:29.514 --> 11:31.505
Yeah.

11:32.784 --> 11:34.718
( Chattering )

11:34.786 --> 11:37.619
This looks great.

11:37.689 --> 11:41.386
Here you go.
One for Burt and one for Ernie.

11:43.829 --> 11:47.356
I'm calling you Ernie now
because you look like the Muppet.

11:47.432 --> 11:49.696
I didn't ask for a drink.

11:49.768 --> 11:52.100
I didn't ask to be born in a field.

11:52.170 --> 11:54.695
But you fought back
against adversity...

11:54.773 --> 11:57.298
just like your Indian brothers.

11:57.376 --> 11:59.674
What is he, Cherokee?

12:03.115 --> 12:05.083
( Singsongy )
Gobble, gobble, gobble.

12:05.150 --> 12:07.209
It's time to carve the turkey.

12:07.286 --> 12:09.516
( Giggling )
Red.

12:09.588 --> 12:12.716
Actually, Kitty,
I think this is Eric's year.

12:12.791 --> 12:17.160
<i>Seems like he's growing up</i>
<i>and finally buckling down.</i>

12:17.229 --> 12:19.891
Here you go, Son.

12:19.965 --> 12:22.092
Wow.

12:22.167 --> 12:24.101
Okay.

12:24.169 --> 12:29.038
Well, in that case, I would like to
make a... kind of announcement.

12:29.107 --> 12:32.440
<i>Check it out.!</i>
<i>I'm bread man.</i>

12:32.511 --> 12:34.479
Shut up! Eric's talking.

12:34.546 --> 12:36.673
Go ahead, honey.

12:37.716 --> 12:39.650
Okay.

12:39.718 --> 12:42.915
Well, I'm really glad
that my family's here and my friends...

12:42.988 --> 12:45.548
and, well, even my math teacher.

12:45.624 --> 12:49.424
Because, uh, something
happened a few days ago that
I'd like to share with everyone.

12:49.494 --> 12:51.325
Eric, we agreed this isn't the time.

12:51.396 --> 12:53.387
- No. No, I meant-
- Not the time for what?

12:53.465 --> 12:56.559
To talk about how he's failing math.

12:57.703 --> 13:01.104
- What?
- Fez, what the hell?

13:02.174 --> 13:05.041
I've been drinking.

13:05.110 --> 13:08.375
Mr. Forman,
you did sign the failing notice.

13:08.447 --> 13:10.711
I didn't sign-

13:10.782 --> 13:13.512
You forged my name?

13:13.585 --> 13:18.955
Wow. I really picked
the right day to come home, huh?

13:22.661 --> 13:24.595
Okay, um...

13:24.663 --> 13:26.654
who likes dark meat?

13:26.732 --> 13:30.566
Hey, who doesn't?
Am I right, ladies?

13:32.270 --> 13:34.363
Oh, Lord.

13:51.723 --> 13:54.556
So you lied to me about school.

13:54.626 --> 13:57.527
Now, it wasn't a lie so much as a...

13:57.596 --> 13:59.621
misdirection, really.

14:01.133 --> 14:03.067
We'll talk about this later.

14:03.135 --> 14:06.502
Well, Laurie, looks like
a seat just opened up for you.

14:06.571 --> 14:08.562
Come on over and grab a biscuit.

14:11.777 --> 14:14.507
Forty-two minutes
and I'm back on top.

14:16.615 --> 14:20.073
