14:20.152 --> 14:22.643
Oh, no. That's what
I wanted to happen.

14:23.655 --> 14:26.317
Burt, honey, pass me your plate.

14:27.793 --> 14:29.761
Burtikins.

14:30.762 --> 14:32.787
- Burt!
- I'm up.

14:33.832 --> 14:35.925
Bob, you know what
Eric's problem is?

14:36.001 --> 14:38.231
All that time he's spending
with your daughter.

14:38.303 --> 14:40.237
Hey, Donna ain't the problem.

14:40.305 --> 14:45.572
Eric's the one who corrupted her up so dirty,
I had to send her to Catholic school.

14:45.644 --> 14:47.976
How could he be failing math?

14:48.046 --> 14:50.514
Kitty, I'm sure
he did the best he could.

14:50.582 --> 14:53.813
For someone who was
held too long as a baby.

14:55.287 --> 14:58.586
I bet that explains
why he hit puberty so late too.

14:58.657 --> 15:01.319
No. That was because
of your mother's smoking.

15:05.697 --> 15:11.101
Fez, I know you've only spoken English
for a couple weeks now, but...

15:11.169 --> 15:14.070
could you have learned the words,
''Don't tell my dad''?

15:14.139 --> 15:16.073
''Don't,'' a contraction
meaning ''do not''...

15:16.141 --> 15:18.701
and ''tell my dad,'' meaning <i>shut up?</i>

15:20.145 --> 15:23.410
Okay, right there,
you just told me not to shut up.

15:23.482 --> 15:26.076
It's a wonder you're not
failing English too.

15:26.151 --> 15:28.619
Crack a book,
you lazy son of a bitch.

15:29.988 --> 15:31.922
So, guys...

15:31.990 --> 15:34.083
Ms. McGee.
( Laughs )

15:34.159 --> 15:37.890
Pretty nice, huh? If they put one of her
in every classroom...

15:37.963 --> 15:41.592
I'd never skip school again,
if you know what I mean.

15:41.666 --> 15:44.100
I mean, I'm doin' it with my teacher!

15:44.169 --> 15:47.297
Oh, shh! It's a secret.

15:48.340 --> 15:50.365
I've never been with a teacher.

15:50.442 --> 15:53.639
But I was with the post-office lady.
That was cool.

15:53.712 --> 15:57.204
I got a hundred free stamps
and a monster roll of tape.

15:57.282 --> 16:00.911
I like older women.
They always got something smart to say.

16:03.121 --> 16:05.487
<i>( Stereo:Soft Rock )</i>

16:05.557 --> 16:09.584
I think I could probably
fit inside of a record player.

16:09.661 --> 16:11.925
That's gotta sound good in there.

16:11.997 --> 16:14.397
Inside of a record player?

16:16.334 --> 16:18.495
I miss dating Kelso.

16:18.570 --> 16:20.561
The guys I'm with now, they're so-

16:20.639 --> 16:22.732
I don't know.
What's the word?

16:22.807 --> 16:25.037
Married.

16:25.110 --> 16:28.637
Hey, <i>you</i> and Kelso didn't date.

16:28.713 --> 16:30.908
You're just a tramp he cheated with.

16:30.982 --> 16:34.543
