16:42.060 --> 16:44.187
who's never been with Kelso.

16:44.262 --> 16:46.389
Which makes me wanna say, ''Ew!''

16:46.464 --> 16:48.694
And also, ''Thank God.''

16:50.135 --> 16:52.126
But you, I mean, you're a teacher.

16:52.203 --> 16:55.001
Can't you get in trouble
for dating a student?

16:55.073 --> 16:57.803
Hey, let 'em come and get me.

16:57.876 --> 16:59.867
He's 1 8.

16:59.945 --> 17:01.879
I make $1 1 ,000 a year.

