17:10.689 --> 17:13.123
So, that was one rootin'-tootin'...

17:13.191 --> 17:15.921
big, old crap of a day, huh?

17:15.993 --> 17:18.019
Yep. Pretty much.

17:18.096 --> 17:20.894
I just really wanted to tell people
that we were engaged.

17:20.965 --> 17:22.900
Know what?
Maybe it'd be easier...

17:22.968 --> 17:25.868
if we just showed up
next Thanksgiving with a kid.

17:28.673 --> 17:30.641
Hey, thanks for dinner, Kitty.

17:30.709 --> 17:33.803
I'll remember to wear
my stretch pants next time.

17:33.878 --> 17:37.109
Oh, let me know
if you find that button.

17:37.182 --> 17:40.913
Good night. I apologize
if my being here upset you.

17:40.986 --> 17:45.389
No, no, no. I- I just feel
you being seen out with a student...

17:45.457 --> 17:48.620
is- it's just awfully bad principle.

17:48.693 --> 17:51.560
He doesn't care.
He's dating a cheerleader.

17:54.132 --> 17:56.794
Burt. Burtie Bear.

17:58.136 --> 18:00.969
- Burt!
- Grandma, let me.

18:03.208 --> 18:05.676
- Grandpa!
- I'm up!

18:07.479 --> 18:10.471
My goodness,
you are going to make some lucky man...

18:10.548 --> 18:12.948
a wonderful wife!

18:13.018 --> 18:15.179
Oh, my God.

18:15.253 --> 18:17.278
That's where Laurie
gets her mean streak.

18:17.355 --> 18:20.415
It's not from delightful me.
It's from my evil mother!

18:21.826 --> 18:23.817
So evil skips a generation.

18:25.463 --> 18:28.591
So that means
that my granddaughter...

18:28.667 --> 18:30.601
is gonna be the devil.

18:30.669 --> 18:33.638
Well, don't worry. Because no woman's
gonna wanna bear your idiot kids...

18:33.705 --> 18:35.696
if you can't even pass math.

18:37.709 --> 18:40.109
How could you forge my signature?

18:40.178 --> 18:43.079
- Here comes yelling.
- Yeah. I don't wanna hear this.

18:43.148 --> 18:45.878
I'll help with the dishes.

18:45.950 --> 18:48.350
And I'll take
these half-empty glasses.

18:48.420 --> 18:51.082
Okay. No, no.
You've had enough.

18:51.156 --> 18:53.090
Eric.

18:53.158 --> 18:55.217
What the hell is wrong with you?

18:55.293 --> 18:57.921
He doesn't understand
consequences, Daddy.

18:57.996 --> 19:00.055
Well, maybe he'll understand this.

19:00.131 --> 19:03.828
From now on, every time
you disobey me...

19:03.902 --> 19:07.099
or lie to me or do anything
that pisses me off...

19:07.172 --> 19:09.333
you're gonna pay me money.

19:10.875 --> 19:14.936
Pay you?
Wait, you're fining me?

19:15.013 --> 19:18.779
It's like giving him tickets
for being dumb.

19:18.850 --> 19:23.412
Okay, okay. I think we're forgetting
about a time-tested punishment.

19:23.488 --> 19:26.582
There's your foot. Here's my ass.
Swing away.

19:27.926 --> 19:29.860
Well, it obviously doesn't work.

19:29.928 --> 19:32.863
So, for forging my name...

19:32.931 --> 19:35.058
you owe me 30 bucks.

19:39.170 --> 19:41.229
Daddy, can I borrow $30?

19:41.306 --> 19:44.070
- Sure, kitten.
- Wha-

19:44.142 --> 19:47.134
Laurie, your grandparents
are sleeping in your room.

19:47.212 --> 19:51.046
So you take Eric's room,
and the math whiz can ride the couch.

19:55.386 --> 19:59.447
Well, another Thanksgiving
come and gone.

19:59.524 --> 20:01.958
Certainly an eventful day, hmm?

20:02.026 --> 20:04.927
Yeah. But with
our ungrateful daughter...

20:04.996 --> 20:08.159
that dumb-ass son...

20:08.233 --> 20:10.861
and a drunk foreign kid, I'd say...

20:12.971 --> 20:15.701
actually, it was
a little better than last year.

20:20.145 --> 20:23.581
- I know we're young.
- But we're totally in love.

20:23.648 --> 20:25.639
And we just want you to know...

20:25.717 --> 20:27.810
- we're engaged!
- We're engaged!

20:32.457 --> 20:34.687
- Feels good to tell someone.
- Yeah.

20:34.759 --> 20:36.750
I think they're happy for us.

20:39.631 --> 20:41.622
Look, Schotzie's celebrating.

